lead_paragraph: England goalkeeper Jack Butland is likely to miss the UEFA European Championship in France this summer after fracturing an ankle during Saturday's 3-2 friendly win over Germany, he said on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: England Keeper Butland Says to Miss Euro 2016 Due to Injury
